---
title: Asian Portabello Mushrooms & Chicken Char Siu Broth with Sweetcorn & Spring Onion
description: A warm soup is something to get excited about for two reasons. First, it’s super easy to make with no fuss and lots
of taste. Second, it’s packed with chicken and mushrooms - simply delicious!

*Unfortunately, this week’s edamame-hemp dumplings were in short supply, so we've replaced them with portabello mushrooms instead. Don’t worry, the recipe will be just as delicious, just be sure to follow your recipe card!*
